topic: ~pastcough keep repeat (cough)

	u: ($present) respond(~currentcough)  ^fail(TOPIC) 
	u: ($family) respond(~familycough) ^fail(TOPIC) 

#! Was your past cough productive
	u: Was_your_past_cough_productive  (was your past cough productive)  ^factanswer("I never had a cough.")
	u: (ever * [produce bring hack] * cough) ^reuse (Was_your_past_cough_productive)
	u: (cough * [productive produce "bring up" phlegm sputum] * [past ever before]) ^reuse (Was_your_past_cough_productive)